---
description: General coding conventions for c0r.AI project
alwaysApply: true
---

- Use Python ≥ 3.10 for bots and webhooks.
- Use TypeScript ≥ 4.5 for Cloudflare Workers.
- Follow PEP8 for Python; Airbnb style for TypeScript.
- Format with Black, Flake8/Ruff for linting.
- Use `.env` for all secrets; never hardcode keys.
- Add clear logging (INFO, ERROR, DEBUG).
- Always after update code also update CHANGELOG.md